ght biography by Jason Ankeny, discography and album reviews, credits & releases] at [[AllMusic]]\n* [https://www.discogs.com/artist/131320-Gary-Wright?limit=500&page=1 Gary Wright discography, album releases & credits] at [[Discogs]]\n* [https://open.spotify.com/artist/3z6Uf5IZkN4TogRpRpgD84 Gary Wright albums to be listened] on [[Spotify]]\n* [https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9jKsnmyIiPHd3VsAGjTn0g Gary Wright albums to be listened] on [[YouTube]]\n* [https://podsodcast.com/2015/11/25/em18/ Career retrospective interview from November 2015 with Pods & Sods] at PodsOdCast.com\n\n{{Gary Wright}}\n{{Spooky Tooth}}\n{{George Harrison}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Wright, Gary}}\n[[Category:1943 births]]\n[[Category:American expatriates in the United Kingdom]]\n[[Category:American hard rock musicians]]\n[[Category:American male singers]]\n[[Category:American new-age musicians]]\n[[Category:American rock keyboardists]]\n[[Category:American soft rock musicians]]\n[[Category:College of William & Mary alumni]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:New York University alumni]]\n[[Category:People from Cresskill, New Jersey]]\n[[Category:Progressive rock keyboardists]]\n[[Category:Spooky Tooth members]]\n[[Category:SUNY Downstate Medical Center alumni]]\n[[Category:Tenafly High School alumni]]\n[[Category:American world music musicians]]\n[[Category:People from Palos Verdes Estates, California]]\n[[Category:American organists]]\n[[Category:Male organists]]\n[[Category:American rock pianists]]\n[[Category:American male pianists]]\n[[Category:A&M Records artists]]\n[[Category:Island Records artists]]\n[[Category:Warner Records artists]]\n[[Category:20th-century American musicians]]\n[[Category:21st-century American musicians]]\n[[Category:20th-century American pianists]]\n[[Category:21st-century American keyboardists]]\n[[Category:21st-century organists]]\n[[Category:20th-century American keyboardists]]\n", "name_user": "2a01:cb14:620:ec00:80ad:1413:4198:c21d",